Description: ===========
        NTPDateTime
        ===========
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/ntpdatetime.svg
                :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/ntpdatetime
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/igroen/ntpdatetime.svg
